item.title: CVE-2017-10930|2024-09-16T17:33:43.111Z -- zte -- zx10%201800-2s
item.description: The ZXR10 1800-2S before v3.00.40 incorrectly restricts access to a resource from an unauthorized actor, resulting in ordinary users being able to download configuration files to steal information like administrator accounts and passwords.
